  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study will be a multicenter randomised controlled trial of the use of irrigation fluid of
      body temperature versus irrigation fluid of room temperature during burr hole evacuation of
      chronic subdural hematoma.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
